wdi2-SL.TLF.TOTL.FE.ZS.def: Female labor force as a percentage of the total show the extent to which women are active in the labor force. Labor force comprises people ages 15 and older who supply labor for the production of goods and services during a specified period.
wdi2-SL.TLF.TOTL.FE.ZS.name: Labor force
wdi2-SL.TLF.TOTL.FE.ZS.source: Derived using data from International Labour Organization, ILOSTAT database. The data retrieved on June 15, 2021.
